&lt;p&gt;For an informal discussion, contact Kathryn Haywood (Primary Care Team Leader) or Paul McArdle (Lead Clinical Dietitian &amp; Deputy Head of Nutrition).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email: kathryn.haywood@bhamcommunity.nhs.uk or paul.mcardle@nhs.net or contact us by phone on 0121 683 2300.&lt;/p&gt;
